Author: SHybrid
Text: I feel it and I hate that too! Sadly it's always going to happen since people know no shit. EDs are as common as they are underrated by the people who don't have one. Averagely, a regular person has in its circle of friends&relatives at least one with ED, yet we talk about it so little.  Anyway, here we say "who minds his own fucks lives a 100 years". The waiter should've done that. And you never be ashamed of cake. Cake is joy. You just brought joy in your life.
